	(text "PSU HT — HIGH VOLTAGE SECTION\n\n1. TR_HT: Antek AN-0T220 (220VAC secondary, 15VA)\n2. BR2: W04G bridge (1A/400V)\n3. RC filter: C_HT1(47µ/400V) → R_HT1(3.3K/3W) → C_HT2(100µ/400V) → R_HT2(1.5K/2W) → C_HT3(100µ/400V)\n4. Bleeders: 470K/2W across each cap\n5. B+ ≈ 270-290V DC\n\nHEATER SECTION\n\n1. Source: +24V regulated rail\n2. LM317T → 12.6V DC (R_adj3=240R, R_adj3b=2.21K + trim 500R)\n3. V1 heater (pins 4-5) → V2 heater (pins 4-5) → GND (series, 150mA)"
		(at 25.4 25.4 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
		(uuid "f2000001-psu-ht-text-000000000001")
	)
)
